{"tid":1937302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日日帶風向，無止境互屌，連登玩完了","createTime":"2020-03-21T20:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T16:09:27.000Z","uid":171506,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5f82b72bdea85054a29e55f6322d761eeb4248","tid":1937302,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:38:05.000Z","msg":"說好的「兄弟爬山」呢？<br />\n<br />\n以中共的人力物力財力，搵幾百個五毛，每人控制10個ac，鍾意點帶風向都得，話黃之鋒係變性人都有人信。<br />\n<br />\n假設五毛月薪2萬，500人要1000萬一個月，一年都係億二，對中共黎講，根本濕濕碎。<br />\n<br />\n臨近立法會選舉，中共請多十倍人都唔出奇，到時日日批鬥黃營候選人，每日老作幾單醜聞，配合紅媒全力抹黑，連登分分鐘仲衰過香討。<br />\n<br />\n可能要諗更加好的討論平台。係咪要好似鹿鼎記入面嘅天地會咁，要有兩個人介紹才可以有login？"},{"pid":"05ab293bcd9c2ae5ac5cdf03e123ff95702889cf","tid":1937302,"uid":325126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:39:42.000Z","msg":"同意 日日咁搞法 乜都傾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0c3c4df40d5364bce29c783b040a00655c63a2","tid":1937302,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"05ab293bcd9c2ae5ac5cdf03e123ff95702889cf","tid":1937302,"uid":325126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:39:42.000Z","msg":"同意 日日咁搞法 乜都傾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:42:22.000Z","msg":"依家連登同香討有乜分別？都係屌黃絲"},{"pid":"2ea8619de399815a8bcf28a11dbb96ba5eddce96","tid":1937302,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abd87cca5bbd71fa364678ceb597026cf3aead90","tid":1937302,"uid":172192,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:49:55.000Z","msg":"五毛滲透效率同admin不作為<br />\n而連登作為全港最大反共討論區亦一直相安無事<br />\n講真 你話連仔已經名存實亡我都信"},{"pid":"629b05582025eadeb2605e7312eae446d14cdb7a","tid":1937302,"uid":184433,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:54:11.000Z","msg":"我睇Facebook 多。會發現兩個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"